cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper proposes a real-time system for mapping indoor environments for sound-related robotics applications. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The proposed method estimates acoustic materials from visual cues using a semantic segmentation CNN network. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on estimating acoustic materials for sound-related robotics applications. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The proposed system integrates acoustic material estimation and mapping in real-time. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with both visual and acoustic information and their integration for mapping.
